    <section>
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Rent A Ride! We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled in a safe and responsible manner. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and protect the data you provide when using our website and services.</p>
        <p>By using Rent A Ride, you consent to the collection and use of your data in accordance with this policy.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect and process the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Car Information</strong>: When you list a car or book a car, we collect data about the car, including:
                <ul>
                    <li>Car model</li>
                    <li>License plate number</li>
                    <li>Location (e.g., car's pickup or return location)</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Booking Information</strong>: When you make a booking, we collect data related to the car and booking details, including:
                <ul>
                    <li>The car model and license plate of the booked car</li>
                    <li>The location of the car</li>
                    <li>The booking date</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Car Listings and Management</strong>: To display car information for users to browse and book.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking Management</strong>: To process and manage car bookings, including the car information and booking date.</li>
            <li><strong>Customer Support</strong>: To respond to inquiries regarding car availability or booking issues.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Compliance</strong>: To comply with applicable laws, regulations, and legal requests.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain the car and booking information only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected. Once no longer necessary, we will securely delete or anonymize your data.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not share your data with third parties except in the following cases:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Service Providers</strong>: We may share your data with third-party service providers who assist in operations such as car listing or booking management.</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements</strong>: We may disclose your information to comply with legal obligations, enforce our terms and conditions, or protect the rights, property, or safety of Rent A Ride, its users, or others.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable precautions to protect your car and booking information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. This includes using secure servers and encryption methods to store and transmit your information.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the following rights regarding your data:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Access</strong>: You can request access to the car and booking data we have stored.</li>
            <li><strong>Correction</strong>: You can update or correct car and booking information at any time through your account settings.</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion</strong>: You can request the deletion of car and booking data by contacting us, subject to certain exceptions (e.g., legal obligations).</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out</strong>: You can opt-out of receiving promotional communications from us by following the instructions in the emails you receive.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>8. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Rent A Ride uses cookies to improve your experience. These cookies allow us to remember your preferences, improve site functionality, and analyze user behavior. By using our website, you consent to the use of cookies as described in our <a href="https://media0.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExbTN4b25xZTU4MThza2V3M3B2cnlweHZveTk4ZDdydmE5dW0ycnM0dyZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/xT0xeMA62E1XIlup68/giphy.gif">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
        <h2>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on this page, along with the effective date of the update.</p>
    </section>
